{"tid":2357114,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(剝智慧齒) 鄧幹耀 定 高如春 好","createTime":"2021-01-07T08:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:31:19.000Z","uid":161095,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf9c0c28afa5a23b4a9e8fd1a049971722e81ac","tid":2357114,"uid":161095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"早幾日去洗牙, 發現左下智慧齒蛀左<br />\n話要剝, 但45度角生, 有少少頂住前面大牙, 又近神經線, 唔肯剝...<br />\n<br />\n上網搵左搵, 連登推介鄧神醫, Google 推介高如春, &quot;傳聞馬頭圍道的高如春牙醫專剝奇難雜症智慧齒&quot;<br />\n究竟邊個好D?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8392a4b7c34b2fd6caed165045915ac9461e72e","tid":2357114,"uid":82938,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"鄧幹耀啦<br />\n我都有兩隻橫生要搵佢剝 不過無蛀無痛又要暑假先得閒剝 最快都暑假先剝"},{"pid":"799cc5e3e9bea9dcd72af91a595c910e23495d25","tid":2357114,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"前者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚牛"},{"pid":"4c14e68ce3b27b15c4db3f5b843056e4d6ef5fe2","tid":2357114,"uid":65910,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"鄧幹耀，勁快"},{"pid":"e7a4bdebca4649482024d5f648620106608c3a7f","tid":2357114,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"高如春算平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508efcb473677e58cc34f27cc6f575c5e4153af3","tid":2357114,"uid":54134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"鄧 我左右兩邊嘅下面都唔夠位生<br />\n搞到打橫生加隻大牙藏咗係隻橫生智慧齒下面<br />\n兩邊都係咁 又近神經線 都係去鄧搞<br />\n又快手 有個姑娘仲幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64604061c5047d28be0171097ac4cb27c5b10e2d","tid":2357114,"uid":29